## 📌 Project Overview

This is a **Rule-Based AI Chatbot** built as the first project of my internship at DecodeLabs. Unlike machine learning chatbots that learn from data, this chatbot uses **pure deterministic logic** - every response is explicitly programmed using if-else logic and dictionary lookups.

### Project Goal
Create a simple rule-based chatbot that responds to predefined user inputs using control flow and decision-making logic.

